column5:
Sometimes I imagine I am dead. But wishing I was alive. I imagine I'm in my coffin, I'm calm but I can see life happening. Then instead of wishing I was dead I wish to be alive. 
If that makes sense.
Watch Martyrs. Overlooked and v messed up!
Here if you want to chat mate. I know how you feel. The physical pain. The mental pain. The constant mind games the mind plays. Message back anytime.
